race.comment: ALL CALM (2) boasts a strong record this journey with six wins and six minors from 15 tries. Below best last time at Goulburn (20.21) in a Grade 3/4, finishing a 7 length fifth. Makes strong appeal on best. ME SPOOK (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (18.44) at this track behind It's Noon in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can feature again. IVY'S MIGHT (8) can measure up with the right run. Something for the Multiples: CONFECTIONERY (4)
